Description:
    Generate the newsletter for the specified month. The newsletter will be created in the `content/announcements` directory with the filename format `YYYY-MM-DD-month-newsletter.md`. The generated newsletter will include a list of events for the specified month, as well as a list of contributors who have merged pull requests during that month.

    **YOU MUST SEED THE DB BEFORE GENERATING THE NEWSLETTER**
    **Run `bin/rails db:seed`.**

Example:
    bin/rails generate newsletter Month

    This will create:
        content/announcements/YYYY-MM-DD-month-newsletter.md
